Description:
  Create a scaffold to implement a ubiquo_widget.

Example:
    rails generate ubiquo:widget Example key:string description:text is_active:boolean

    This will create:
      controller code: app/widgets/NAME_widget.rb
      public partials: app/views/widgets/NAME/_show.html.erb
      ubiquo partials: app/views/widgets/NAME/ubiquo/_form.html.erb
      widget class:    app/models/widgets/NAME.rb
